3.  <span data-ttu-id="1cbed-145">Затем вызывается механизм визуализации речи с измененным <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> массива.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1cbed-145">A speech rendering engine is then called with the modified <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> array.</span></span>  
  
