 <span data-ttu-id="1cbed-162">В приведенном ниже примере является частью реализации синтеза настраиваемое преобразование речи, наследование <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>и с помощью применения <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState>, и <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1cbed-162">The example below is part of a custom speech synthesis implementation inheriting from <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>, and using the use of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState>, and <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId></span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="1cbed-163">Реализация <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1cbed-163">The implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span></span>  
  
